Content-Type: multipart/alternative; 
              boundary="---- message03boundary ----"

------ message03boundary ----
Content-Type: text/html

<p>... a <HTML> body goes here ...</p>

------ message03boundary ----
Content-Type: text/plain

... while this is a plain version of the same ...

------ message03boundary ------

------ main boundary ------

